@AOC You are something. 
1st you spread gossip & innuendo. 
Then the POTUS makes proposals. 
Then at the stroke of midnight Pelosi  writes a bill & immediately it should be passed. 
 The Democrats have politicized the Coronavirus.
Partisan politics. Democrats grandstanding. https://t.co/fmt6gtSgDx
